{"tid":2329432,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己跟唔上毒撚界","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T19:29:14.000Z","uid":48042,"like":49,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"f1080177091962604dcb68c70d83a43ea9617e58","tid":2329432,"uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"自從Vtuber hit咗之後 開始跟唔到毒撚fd啲話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前大家都係傾有咩動畫 漫畫好睇 <br />\n<br />\n有咩game好玩<br />\n<br />\n近期開始多左vtuber呢樣野 兩邊不是人<br />\n<br />\n個個開始討論邊個Vtuber好睇 一陣追邊個邊個 <br />\n<br />\n邊個邊個又有咩八卦<br />\n<br />\n聽到我一頭霧水 「乜撚嘢啊」完全搭唔到嗲 <br />\n<br />\n自己試過開幾個直播嚟睇 但係好快就quit <br />\n<br />\n自問融入唔到呢種文化 加上自己唔多識日文 <br />\n<br />\n雖然聽得明少少 但get唔到好睇個位 <br />\n<br />\n可能只係我唔識欣賞 <br />\n<br />\n可能係我呢啲老毒撚唔肯接受新事物<br />\n<br />\n但願我呢啲老毒撚日後唔會因為唔睇Vtuber <br />\n<br />\n而受其他有睇嘅毒撚歧視<br />\n<br />\n媽的貢丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f209e7183b6a5923aba34be3c259350ac93da34","tid":2329432,"uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229c82b5681da1da2a02d9f41efbb2cb0753c624","tid":2329432,"uid":8307,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:42:10.000Z","msg":"我個仔返學個陣話冇睇vtuber埋唔到堆<br />\n點知我呢排搵到新工都係冇睇vtuber埋唔到堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdde1bf68a93503499e377e05c276e4a9c629e1","tid":2329432,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"珍"},{"pid":"432876894e03a26ba34983724744cd83abb56dfe","tid":2329432,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"2d9bb04e130d7a04892c0f06cb58c294cff14624","tid":2329432,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"冇毒撚fd"},{"pid":"7a6450781ece3d49eb6d87071bdbd7fc0cd9089c","tid":2329432,"uid":8307,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"初頭個啲咩holo炎上,咁大單新聞<br />\n都叫答到兩句嗲<br />\n每日返去碌下啲資訊R水吹<br />\n點知佢地啲話題根本跟唔上,一時又講咩彩虹咩個人勢<br />\n有咩慘得過讀完書每晚都要搵書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b00d666c60deeae7ebc97edabecd2c8437d49d","tid":2329432,"uid":9151,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"睇vt 真係好撚毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2d1d9c141cc31175ded63c2208c527aa1278c1","tid":2329432,"uid":345520,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"放心樓主我都唔識欣賞vtuber, 本身覺得冇咩野，但係之前見到有條片係有啲fans捐成舊水美金只係為咗叫個vtuber眨一下眼，嗰一刻我已經知道自己跟唔上宅界"},{"pid":"c8b1ae08b5d959e039d0dd63c66fb6117f2c8a69","tid":2329432,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦傻仔"},{"pid":"7efc18e4195c0e30f3d590711155965062deafed","tid":2329432,"uid":105678,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:50:47.000Z","msg":"有冇睇vtuber其實睇得出一個人係真毒定偽毒MK<br />\n<br />\n好似啲娛樂台啲弱智追星族咁，關注住班vtuber嘅一舉一動，小小事又懶係大新聞咁<br />\n<br />\n唔係話睇動漫就唔畀做V豚，但可以反映出一個毒撚究竟係想喺動漫度尋求認同感定真心「宅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37bac2c2d3e1327c47e2134b4831bbbd507910f","tid":2329432,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b1ae08b5d959e039d0dd63c66fb6117f2c8a69","tid":2329432,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦傻仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"比啲面我個FD好喎"},{"pid":"92ffe2278142e186e7df2bec8f048e4437e6887d","tid":2329432,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"咁咪quit lor<br />\n興趣都係想開心姐"},{"pid":"c03c0963c90c338b81bb2a75f0c84da155bdda00","tid":2329432,"uid":146340,"l